reviewText: I am completely surprised at the quality of the sound since it is from 1991! The musicianship is spectacular, which is to be expected.  The four main dudes, Steve, David, Jeff, and Mike have always been amazing. You will not be disappointed if you're a TOTO fan.
The bluray is great. Wonderful sound and video.
I'm a big Steve Lukather fan.  He is a great guitar player and very underrated as a singer.
Fantastic - last concert to see Jeff & Mike Porcaro play together - great show. Concert for the ages...we will remember those guys!
